---
title: Chicken, Tofu & Sweet Chilli Veggie Stir-Fry with Egg Noodles & Crushed Peanuts
description: Tonight, we’re frying these soft little tofu cubes, later to be tossed through oodles of egg noodles with veggies and a
too-good-to-be-true sweet chilli stir-fry sauce. With a sprinkling of peanuts on top for crunch, it’s a gold star from us!
